    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, showroom-quality vehicle that stands as a testament to meticulous ownership. This car has been pampered in a climate-controlled environment since day one, and its condition is indistinguishable from new. The exterior finish is flawless, boasting a deep, glass-like luster entirely free of stone chips, swirl marks, or door dings. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary of perfection; the premium leather is supple and uncreased, the carpets are pristine, and it retains that unmistakable new-car scent. Every switch, dial, and digital display functions with crisp precision. Under the hood, the engine bay is immaculate, reflecting a rigorous maintenance schedule performed exclusively by master technicians using genuine parts. The undercarriage is equally impressive, showing no signs of inclement weather use. For the buyer seeking an investment-grade example that requires absolutely no excuses, this is the definitive choice.",
      "price": 48500.0,
